                                                  Student Management System

Objective: Build a Java application using JDBC to manage student records.

Features:
    Add a student
    View all students
    Search student by ID
    Update student details
    Delete a student

Database Table:
    Student ID
    Name
    Age
    Department
    Email

Concepts To Be Used:
    JDBC Connection
    PreparedStatement
    ResultSet
    CRUD Operations
    Exception Handling
